                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-badge">COMMERCIAL SERVICES</div>
                            <h2>Trimesh Drone Solutions</h2>
                            <p>Professional drone operations for commercial, industrial, and data-driven projects</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="contact-card-body">
                            <h3>Services Include:</h3>
                            <ul class="contact-services-list">
                                <li>Aerial Inspections & Mapping</li>
                                <li>Construction Documentation</li>
                                <li>2D/3D Surveying & Modeling</li>
                                <li>Infrastructure Analysis</li>
                                <li>Thermal Imaging (Coming Soon)</li>
                            </ul>

                            <div class="contact-details">
                                <div class="contact-detail-item">
                                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
