                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Additional Contact Info -->
        <section class="contact-info-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Other Ways to Reach Us</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9C13.039 21.275 12.535 21.487 12.008 21.487C11.481 21.487 10.977 21.275 10.602 20.9L6.343 16.657C5.22422 15.5381 4.46234 14.1127 4.15369 12.5608C3.84504 11.009 4.00349 9.40047 4.60901 7.93868C5.21452 6.4769 6.2399 5.22749 7.55548 4.34846C8.87107 3.46943 10.4178 3 12 3C13.5822 3 15.1289 3.46943 16.4445 4.34846C17.7601 5.22749 18.7855 6.4769 19.391 7.93868C19.9965 9.40047 20.155 11.009 19.8463 12.5608C19.5377 14.1127 18.7758 15.5381 17.657 16.657Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M12 13C13.6569 13 15 11.6569 15 10C15 8.34315 13.6569 7 12 7C10.3431 7 9 8.34315 9 10C9 11.6569 10.3431 13 12 13Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Location</h3>
                        <p>Austin, Texas</p>
                        <p class="info-detail">Serving the greater Austin metro area with free travel within 20 miles</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M12 8V12L15 15M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Business Hours</h3>
                        <p>Monday - Saturday: 8:00 AM - 7:00 PM</p>
                        <p class="info-detail">Emergency response available 24/7 for qualified scenarios</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-icon">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M9 12L11 14L15 10M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>FAA Certified</h3>
                        <p>Part 107 Certified Pilot</p>
                        <p class="info-detail">Fully insured and compliant with all FAA regulations</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <section class="faq-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                    <p class="section-subtitle">Quick answers to common questions</p>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-grid">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>What's your typical turnaround time?</h3>
                        <p>Most projects are delivered within 48-72 hours. Real estate media can often be delivered within 24 hours, and we offer expedited service for urgent needs.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>How far do you travel?</h3>
                        <p>We offer free travel within 20 miles of Austin. For 20-50 miles, there's a $35 travel fee. Custom quotes available for projects beyond 50 miles.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>What equipment do you use?</h3>
                        <p>Our fleet includes DJI Mavic 3 Pro for professional operations and Mini 2 SE for specialized applications. All equipment is maintained to the highest standards.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>Do you provide raw footage?</h3>
                        <p>Raw footage can be provided upon request for an additional fee. Standard deliverables include edited, color-graded content ready for your use.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>Are you insured?</h3>
                        <p>Yes! We carry comprehensive liability insurance and are FAA Part 107 certified. All operations comply with federal and local regulations.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <h3>Can you fly in any weather?</h3>
                        <p>Safety is our priority. We monitor weather conditions closely and will reschedule if conditions aren't suitable. No additional charges for weather delays.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Social Connect Section -->
        <section class="social-connect-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Connect With Us</h2>
                <p>Follow our latest projects and industry insights on social media</p>
                
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Bluesky">
                        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M12 2.247c-2.32 0-5.947 1.935-7.39 6.32-.368 1.119-.61 2.748-.61 4.643 0 .796.055 1.536.148 2.21 1.155 8.421 6.29 8.58 7.862 8.58s6.707-.159 7.862-8.58c.093-.674.148-1.414.148-2.21 0-1.895-.242-3.524-.61-4.643C17.947 4.182 14.32 2.247 12 2.247z" fill="currentColor"/>
                        </svg>
